# speckit.plan
# HOW — Architecture & Approach
# Project: Todo AI Chatbot

---

## Folder Structure

```
todo-AI-chatbot/
├── backend/
│   ├── models.py       # REQ-01 — SQLModel DB models
│   ├── database.py     # REQ-01 — DB engine & session
│   ├── mcp_server.py   # REQ-02 — MCP tools
│   ├── agent.py        # REQ-03 — Groq agent
│   ├── main.py         # REQ-04 — FastAPI app & chat endpoint
│   ├── requirements.txt
│   └── .env            # GROQ_API_KEY, DATABASE_URL
├── frontend/
│   ├── index.html      # REQ-05 — Chat UI
│   ├── style.css       # REQ-05 — Styling
│   └── script.js       # REQ-05 — API integration
├── specs/
│   ├── mcp_tools.md
│   └── agent_behavior.md
├── speckit.constitution
├── speckit.specify
├── speckit.plan        # this file
└── speckit.tasks
```

---

## Request Flow

```
Frontend (index.html/script.js)
    │  POST /api/{user_id}/chat
    ▼
FastAPI (main.py)
    ├── Get/create Conversation in DB
    ├── Fetch Message history from DB
    ├── Store user Message in DB
    ▼
Groq Agent (agent.py)
    ├── System prompt + history + new message
    ├── Groq API call with tool definitions
    ▼
MCP Tools (mcp_server.py)
    ├── add_task / list_tasks / complete_task / delete_task / update_task
    ▼
Neon PostgreSQL (database.py + models.py)
    ▼
Agent returns response to main.py
    ├── Store assistant Message in DB
    └── Return ChatResponse to frontend
```

---

## Key Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| AI provider | Groq | Free tier, fast, supports tool calling |
| MCP integration | In-process (not subprocess) | Simpler, no IPC overhead |
| Tool calling | Groq function calling API | Native support, no extra framework |
| Frontend | Plain HTML/CSS/JS | No build tools, no npm, fully free |
| DB | Neon PostgreSQL | Free tier, serverless, compatible with SQLModel |

---

## Environment Variables

| Variable | Description |
|---|---|
| GROQ_API_KEY | From console.groq.com (free) |
| DATABASE_URL | Neon PostgreSQL connection string (free tier) |
